1. *Vreme* je za mene vrlo va≈æno. (Time is very important for me.)
2. *Vremenske* prilike su se promenile. (The weather conditions have changed.)
3. Nisam imao *vremena* da ispunim svoj obaveze. (I didn't have time to fulfill my obligations.)
4. On je rano ustao kako bi iskoristio *vreme*. (He got up early to make the most of his time.)
5. Ona je spremna da bude na raspolaganju u bilo kom *vremenu*. (She is ready to be available at any time.)